"""
Git commit message template and guidelines for OmniSight
"""

# Format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore
# Examples:
# feat(api): add video upload endpoint
# fix(detection): correct YOLO model loading
# docs(architecture): update component diagram
# test(search): add semantic search tests

# Body (optional, wrap at 72 chars)
# - Explain what was changed and why
# - One item per bullet point

# Footer (optional)
# Closes #123
